|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[l.l_linestatus]], aggr=[[sum(o.o_totalprice)]]                                                                         |
|               |       Projection: o.o_totalprice, l.l_linestatus                                                                                                |
|               |         Inner Join: o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey                                                                                                 |
